name: Burnt Ranch School
description: Burnt Ranch School is one of the most popular places to play pickleball in Burnt Ranch, CA. There are 2 outdoor courts. The lines are permanent, but you'll need to bring your own net. The courts are free.

name: Lewiston Community Center
description: Lewiston Community Center is one of the most popular places to play pickleball in Lewiston, CA. There are 2 outdoor concrete courts. The lines are permanent, but you'll need to bring your own net. Amenities include restrooms and lights. The courts are free.

name: Lowden Park Tennis Courts
description: Four dedicated pickleball courts and two with permanent lines over the tennis court and portable nets.  Lights available until 10:00 p.m.  Call for combination.
